comments: Vucevic (ORL) sets the pick in Bridges's (PHX) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bridges (PHX) and Vucevic (ORL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Booker (PHX) initiates marginal contact with Fournier (ORL) before Fournier hooks Booker's arm, preventing him from disengaging from the contact and affecting his ability to defend the play.
Fultz (ORL) makes marginal contact with Rubio's (PHX) body during his drive and does not prevent him from gathering the ball.
Rubio (PHX) makes incidental contact with Fultz's (ORL) hand on the ball as he dislodges the ball in transition.
Fournier (ORL) initiates some contact with Ayton (PHX) as he goes over the pick, but the contact is marginal.
Ross (ORL) absorbs contact as Rubio (PHX) veers from his path, and the contact with Rubio's body is marginal during the driving shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) sets the screen in Fournier's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ayton (PHX) is firming up in a picking position in Fournier's (ORL) path when contact occurs, and he absorbs the contact.
Bridges (PHX) and Ross (ORL) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Booker (PHX) wraps Vucevic (ORL) in the post.
Rubio (PHX) cleanly dislodges the ball from Vucevic (ORL) in the post.
Fultz (ORL) commits a take foul on Rubio (PHX).
Vucevic (ORL) is not established in a screening position in Rubio's (PHX) path, but Rubio steps around him as he continues moving and any contact is marginal.
Ayton (PHX) is in a legal guarding position and Fournier (ORL) creates the marginal contact by jumping into him.
Iwundu (ORL) commits a take foul on Oubre Jr. (PHX).
Oubre Jr. (PHX) makes incidental contact with Fournier's (ORL) arm after making contact with the ball in transition.
